a-label="Bats" data-stat="pass_batted_passes" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes batted by a defender at or behind the line of scrimmage">Bats</th> <th aria-label="ThAwy" data-stat="pass_throwaways" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes thrown away">ThAwy</th> <th aria-label="Spikes" data-stat="pass_spikes" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes spiked to stop the clock ">Spikes</th> <th aria-label="Drops" data-stat="pass_drops" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes dropped">Drops</th> <th aria-label="Drop%" data-stat="pass_drop_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of passes dropped per pass attempt, excluding spikes and throwaways" data-filter="1" data-name="">Drop%</th> <th aria-label="BadTh" data-stat="pass_poor_throws" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Poor throws">BadTh</th> <th aria-label="Bad%" data-stat="pass_poor_throw_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip sort_default_asc hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of poor throws per pass attempt, excluding spikes and throwaways" data-filter="1" data-name="">Bad%</th> <th aria-label="OnTgt" data-stat="pass_on_target" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="On-target throws, would have hit the intended receiver">OnTgt</th> <th aria-label="OnTgt%" data-stat="pass_on_target_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of on-target throws per pass attempt, excluding spikes and throwaways" data-filter="1" data-name="">OnTgt%</th> <th aria-label="PktTime" data-stat="pocket_time" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Average time the QB had in the pocket between the snap and throwing the ball or pressure collapses the pocket, in seconds" data-filter="1" data-name="">PktTime</th> <th aria-label="Bltz" data-stat="pass_blitzed" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Times blitzed">Bltz</th> <th aria-label="Hrry" data-stat="pass_hurried" scope="col" clas